## Summary
The Anomaly + Forecast feature in Amplitude helps users identify statistically significant deviations in metrics by highlighting anomalies based on historical data and projecting future trends, available in Event Segmentation, Conversion over Time, User Sessions, Retention over Time, and Stickiness charts for Growth and Enterprise plan users.

